      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just \"difficult times\" though. i'm not talking about a bad quarter or a lost promotion. i'm talking about being a pariah. the person i was is dead. the version of me that people respected, the one that actually mattered... that's just gone. how do you even tell someone to \"reach out\" when you feel like there's nothing left of you to offer? there's no version of the future where this is okay. it's just a hollow shell now.",
